full_title_text: In Rio de Janeiro my brakes were cut. In Mexico l was slipped psilocybin while fighting a pack of jaguars. And now, in SHANGHAI… < I'VE GOT YOU! GO LIMP! > * < THIS DOESN'T --MY POLYETHYLENE LINES ARE IMPOSSIBLE TO BREAK! > < BUT NOT IMPOSSIBLE… > <… TO CUT. > It's HIM. < I KNOW THE POLICE ARE AFTER ME FOR MY " SKYSPIDER " STUNTS. BUT WHY YOU? > Jealousy? Some sick game? If he's HERE, he must have… Dammit. I should have figured it out based on SKYSPIDER'S mask… < QIU. HAVE YOU TRAINED ANYONE ELSE LATELY? > < I… YEAH. > < A GUY AROUND YOUR AGE. COULDN'T PLACE HIS ACCENT. > < CALLED HIMSELF "ANTON." > He didn't even bother to use a DIFFERENT fake name… … because he wants me to know he's one step ahead of me. Like in DUBLIN. Or METROPOLIS. Or MOROCCO. Where he ended the life of our master Ouahbi once he realized he was training a PSYCHOPATH. I miss my friend. I miss who I thought he was. He haunts me now, like a ghost, as I near the finish line. My mission has always been about saving people, but Anton… … I'm afraid one day he might kill me. He has all my skills, but his mind has no distractions, whereas mine… I have FEAR. I'm afraid I won't be able to save myself and this mission will end and I'll join my parents in the ground. So I need to visit one more MASTER… … to make my MIND ready. To make me COLD AND TERRIFYING. To make me a creature of the NIGHT. PLEASE, COME IN, MR. WAYNE…

YOU MEAN-- WE WILL TRAVEL THERE, TO THE TOP OF THE GREAT MOUNTAIN, AND SET UP DEFENSES. YOU WANT TO WAIT FOR YOUR DOOM? NO. WE MUST TAKE THE FIGHT TO WHAT THREATENS US, SUPERSAUR! WE DO NOT KNOW HOW STRONG THIS THREAT IS! WE CAN'T JUST MARCH IN-THE RISK IS TOO GREAT! BESIDES, WE DON'T EVEN KNOW WHERE THIS EVIL IS! WELL, THEN LET'S MAKE THEM TELL THE TRUTH. HEY! TELL US, GIGANTA! WHERE IS YOUR MASTER?! THE… CENTER OF THE JUNGLE. WHERE THE TREES DO NOT GROW, AND THE INSECTS DO NOT TREAD. IT CAN ONLY BE VIEWED FROM ABOVE, BUT IT IS BELOW. A DARK MAGIC GUARDS ITS LOCATION FROM THE CREATURES THAT WALK ON THE GROUND. EVEN WITH THE LASSO, YOU SPEAK IN RIDDLES! TELL US WHERE IT IS! IT IS USELESS! HE HAS USED ALL OF US FOR HIS DARK PURPOSE… WHICH IS ALMOST FULFILLED. HE IS COMING… … FOR ALL OF US. BUT HE WILL BE STOPPED. BY ALL OF US. MAYBE HE'LL BE STOPPED BY YOU. BUT I WILL NOT BE THERE. WHAT?! HE WILL FIND A WAY… ALWAYS… ALWAYS FINDS A WAY… THAT GREAT EVIL IS SOMEHOW CONNECTED TO THE JOKERZARD. AND IF I HUNT THAT EVIL… CHANCES ARE I WILL FIND HIS MINIONS… … INCLUDING THE ONE THAT KILLED MY… … I MUST GO. THANK YOU, CHILD. YOU ARE LEARNING. SHE SHOULD BE HERE. WITH US. SHE'S BEEN THROUGH ENOUGH THAT SHE HAS GROWN A STRONG MIND. SHE SHOULD DECIDE FOR HERSELF. WONDERDON AND I NEED YOUR STRENGTH, BATSAUR. PLEASE…. DO NOT LEAVE US LIKE THIS. YOU PRETEND THAT WE ARE FRIENDS, BUT I DO NOT KNOW EITHER OF YOU. YOU ARE MERELY MORE OBSTACLES ON MY PATH TO REVENGE. AND WHEN YOU GET YOUR REVENGE… WILL YOU BE WHOLE? MORE SO THAN I AM NOW. WHERE WILL YOU GO? GIGANTA SAID, IN ORDER TO FIND THIS EVIL'S LOCATION, I HAD TO SEE IT FROM UP HIGH. THIS WILL GET US THERE. COME, CHILD… … LET'S GO FIND JOKERZARD! SUPERSAUR, WE MUST MOVE THE PEOPLE TO THE GREAT MOUNTAIN. SOMETHING TELLS ME WE'RE RUNNING OUT OF TIME. DEAR MOTHER, THE DINOSAURS HERE BICKER CONSTANTLY. THERE IS DISUNITY. NO ONE TRUSTS EACH OTHER. IT MAKES ME MISS TRIMYSCIRA AND HOW WE COULD GIVE IN TO EACH OTHER COMPLETELY WITH NO FEAR OF BETRAYAL. WE ARE MAKING DEFENSES AND PREPARING FOR THIS UNKNOWN TERROR TO COME. BUT I KNOW IT IS NOT ENOUGH. I MUST RALLY THESE GREAT DINOSAURS TO A HIGHER CAUSE. BUT HOW CAN I, WITH DEATH SO NEAR? HOW CAN I INSPIRE WITH ONLY A BONE SWORD AND SHIELD? < MY SON.> * < HELLO, FATHER. > < FATHER… AM I WEAK? > < WEAK? WHATEVER DO YOU MEAN? > < SHOULD I HAVE LEFT WITH BATSAUR? IS MY JOB TO HUNT ALL EVIL? EVERYWHERE? > < I… I DON'T KNOW, MY BOY. > <… BUT ONE THING I DO KNOW… IS HOW GOOD YOU ARE. INSIDE AND OUT. > <THEY NEED TO SEE THAT. THE WHOLE WORLD NEEDS TO SEE. AND… YOU CAN'T CHANGE THE WORLD IF YOU STAY HERE. > < BUT DAD… YOU AND MOM ARE HERE. I CAN'T LEAVE YOU. I HAVE TO KEEP YOU SAFE.> <YOU MUSTN'T WORRY YOURSELF OVER US TOO MUCH. WE CAN TAKE CARE OF OURSELVES. YOU'VE TAUGHT US HOW STRONG WE ARE.> < I KNOW YOU'LL DO THE RIGHT THING.> WHAT MADNESS IS THIS-- BEING THRASHED BY SOME WORTHLESS EGG?! #WHOM! WHOM! WHOM! DO YOUR WORST! FINISH IT ALREADY! HANG ON, AQUANYX! MY BROTHERS! COME ON, I'LL GET YOU OUTTA HERE WHILE TORCH GIVES US COVER. OH NO! WHY DID YOU BRING JOKERZARD AND REVERSE-SLASH WITH YOU? WE DIDN'T WANT THEM TO CAUSE ANY MORE TROUB- #AIEEE! NO, MY MASTER, PLEA-- #MUNCH! MUNCH! #GLUPS! THE TIME HAS COME TO HATCH. STOP GAWKING AND GET US OUT OF HERE, BROTHERS! LET'S GO! #GRRRPP!  GRRRPP! FUEL FROM THE WEAKLINGS ON THIS PITIFUL EARTH… THE LIFE ENERGY FROM MY OWN WARRIORS… ..HAS FINALLY LED TO MY TRUE FORM! I KNOW THE BEINGS OF THIS WORLD ARE TRYING TO RISE AGAINST ME… … BUT I WILL CRUSH THEM IN DUE TIME! FOR MY FIRST TASK... … I MUST REMOVE THIS WORLD OF THEIR GODS! TRIMYSCIRA! DARKYLOSEID IS COMING FOR YOU!

full_title_text: " Tell me another story, Momma. " " What kind of story, Eleanor? " " One about John. " Tell me how he became the Guardian. " " Well, your brother doesn't like to talk about it much. You know that. " Nuh-uh. " " A marine is a kind of soldier. " Before long, John and a lot of other soldiers got sent across the ocean to fight a war. " No! Kyle! " And while he was there… just like every war that ever was… "… something terrible happened. " #YAAARRRRRGGH! " Bad enough that John did something he wasn't in the habit of doing back then. " KYLE! Jason, it's too late! " He prayed. " John. John, We need you. " He prayed for the strength to save the people who needed him. " And in a flash of light, where your brother stood… " … there stood an invincible knight, his eyes blazing with the light of heaven. That's how your brother became a superhero, sweetie. Earth's first and greatest. After the Battle of Oa, he founded a team of Lanterns called the Watchtower to protect Earth while he flew all over the Multiverse. Isn't that nice? #Uh-huh. Enough, all right? I'm working on it. Can I stop hearing about it, please? You're only hearing about it because you're sneaking around back there instead of working. Nobody's sneaking! Can't I take a minute to look at my girls? One day, when he'd done what he set out to do, he took off his ring, and passed it on. He became an architect, like he'd always wanted. And now we all live here together in the house he built for us, and he's finally putting up a fence to keep the rabbits out of my flowers. Just pretend I'm not here, all right? #Hmm. What about the war, Momma? What if the… … th-the… JOHN. JOHN. WE NEED YOU. Rayner? Is that you? THEY'VE FOUND HER, JOHN. MANY OF US HAVE FALLEN. THE BRIGHT REVENANT IS WITH THEM. What, Momma? Did something happen again? I-it's nothing, sweetie. Why don't you practice your reading for a bit? I need to talk to your brother. You told me you formed the Watchtower so they wouldn't need you anymore. That you were done fighting. It's nothing to worry about. The Corps just needs a hand with-- Don't talk to me like I'm stupid, John. She said, " They found her. " You gave me back the daughter I buried. The same age she was when I lost her, and she hasn't aged a day since then.  I know a miracle like that has to be paid back someday. Tell me the truth, John… … is that day today? They're called the Radiant Dead. They're the ones that killed the Old Guardians. If they'd killed the Central Battery like they meant to, there wouldn't be a Corps anymore… probably nothing else, either. So I took the battery from Oa, and I hid it… … in the shape of my baby sister. It really is still her, Mom. My memory of her, anyway. She's just… more than she used to be. Don't worry. I'll fix this. I'll never forget what you did for your sister. But swear to me you'll come back, too. I will. I'll come back. You'll never have to bury either of us again. I've gotta leave for a bit, kiddo. But I won't be long. Take care of your momma, yeah? Okay. And keep practicing your reading. You know We love hearing you read. I know. I'll be right back. And I'll finish that fence. Where's John going, Momma? He's going to do what he does, sweetie. The things no one else can do. " What do you mean, 'no one else'?' Cause John was a soldier? " " Some people think so. His way of never quitting… his mind for strategy, the way he leads people. " But no, that's not why. " John's special because he's a builder. " His mind has always pushed against the limitations that were set on him. " Limitations of resources, or time… even the rules of three-dimensional space. " With his mind, his will, and the power he's been given, he can do anything. "… is that he was looking for the ring before he knew it existed. " My boy's been the Guardian since the day he was born. " " But he's not limited anymore. " What makes him special, even among the other Lanterns… The Guardian is with us! " And whether any of us like it or not… ” "… there are some threats only he can face. " John! Sit-rep, Natasha. Does this situation not speak for itself? An hour ago, we had 2,300 Lanterns! We're down to barely a thousand! 932! You should've called me earlier. You're retired! It's okay. We're gonna get them all back. If the big one gets any closer to the Battery, it's gonna-- Oh god. It's happening. Everybody fall back! The BRIGHT REVENANT is awake! It's headed for Earth! It's after the Battery. I've got him. You've…? What, alone?! John, it'll kill you! You're not wrong to be afraid, kid. But you're wrong to let them see it. We're Lanterns. Let our enemies fear us. I know what you are. I know how old you are and how strong. I know you've killed the greatest heroes and gods of a thousand worlds. But this isn't their home you're threatening now. It's mine. The Guardian! All hail the Guardian! Hail John Stewart! " Your brother was the greatest of all time. He always will be. " But he did his time as a superhero. " Like all the heroes in the old stories, his works of war are done. Now he's doing his works of peace. Will the monsters come back, Momma? Will they try to take me away again? No, sweetie. With your brother John around… "… we'll never be apart again. " IT'S BEEN THREE YEARS. THREE YEARS OF RESEARCH. THREE YEARS OF TRACKING DOWN LEGENDS AND MYTHS. ALL LEADING HERE… … THE TEMPLE OF LIFE. AND THE TWO MEN WITH ME? ABOUT AS TRUSTWORTHY AS SOMEONE WITH THE LAST NAME LUTHOR. BUT LIKE LUTHOR, THEY'D DO ANYTHING FOR CASH. NOW? WHICH IS GREAT, BECAUSE I DIDN'T FEEL LIKE CARRYING THE BAGS. BAGS I'M SURE THEY THINK THEY'LL FILL WITH TREASURE AFTER THEY GET RID OF ME. BOY, DID THEY GET THAT WRONG. MY NAME IS KENDRA SAUNDERS, SOMETIMES KNOWN AS HAWKGIRL. AND I'M NOT DYING TODAY. TODAY IS THE FIRST DAY OF THE REST OF MY LIFE. I'M SURE THESE GOONS'LL BE OKAY. I MEAN, IT'S NOT LIKE THE JUNGLE IS TEEMING WITH POISONOUS ANIMALS, BUGS, SNAKES… OH WAIT. BUT THEY MIGHT FARE BETTER WITH THOSE THAN WHAT'S IN HERE. IT'S CALLED THE TEMPLE OF LIFE, BUT IT'S REALLY ANYTHING BUT. EXACTLY WHAT I NEED. I KNOW. SOUNDS STRANGE. BUT SO IS MY LIFE… OR LIVES, AS IT WERE. I'VE ACTUALLY BEEN REINCARNATED HUNDREDS OF TIMES. AND WHAT'S EVEN WILDER, I REMEMBER EACH OF THOSE LIVES. SOUNDS FUN, RIGHT? TO KEEP COMING BACK? KNOWING IF I LANDED IN A PIT LIKE THESE GUYS BELOW ME, I'D JUST APPEAR IN A NEW BODY, READY TO TRY AGAIN. LIKE SOME SORT OF MYSTICAL VIDEO GAME WITH INFINITE LIVES. BUT WHAT I THOUGHT WAS A BLESSING TURNED OUT TO BE A CURSE. A BURDEN. I REALIZED THAT NO MATTER WHAT I DID, IT WAS SOMETHING I HAD DONE BEFORE. A LIFE OF PERPETUAL SAMENESS. I WAS NO LONGER UNIQUE. I WASN'T EVEN A PERSON. NOT REALLY. I WAS… A VESSEL WAITING TO BE EMPTIED AND FILLED UP AGAIN AND AGAIN… IT'S LIKE DA VINCI SAID, " I THOUGHT I WAS LEARNING TO LIVE. I WAS ONLY LEARNING TO DIE. " BUT TODAY THAT CHANGES. TODAY I GET MY LIFE BACK. I GET MY MORTALITY. AND NOTHING… IS GOING TO STOP ME! NOT EVEN ANCIENT DEATH TRAPS. THERE IT IS. THE VASE OF MORTALITY. LEGEND HAS IT THAT AN ANCIENT GOD-KING CREATED THE WORLD AND MADE EVERYTHING IN IT IN HIS IMAGE-IMMORTAL. NOTHING DIED, AND BECAUSE OF IT, NOTHING LIVED. THE BEAUTY OF THE WORLD THAT WAS ONCE SO VIBRANT, OVER TIME, TURNED DULL. THE GOD'S SON AND DAUGHTER TOLD THE GOD-KING HE WAS WRONG TO MAKE THE WORLD LIKE THEM, AND THE KING AGREED. HE CRIED A RIVER OF TEARS, WHICH FILLED THE EARTH. AND WHEN THE TEARS RECEDED, THE ANIMALS AND PLANTS HAD REGAINED THEIR LUSTER. THEY KNEW THAT THEIR LIVES WOULD END, AND THEREFORE, THEY HAD BETTER GET TO LIVING THEM. NO MORE PAST. NO MORE FUTURE, NO MORE " DESTINY. " JUST TODAY. JUST THE CHANCE TO MAKE MY OWN DECISIONS. TO CHOOSE MY OWN RELATIONSHIPS. TO SOMEDAY PASS AWAY KNOWING THAT I WAS UNIQUE TO MYSELF. A SNOWFLAKE NEVER TO BE SEEN AGAIN. I WAS SPECIAL. YOU DO THIS, KENDRA, THAT'S IT. YOU'VE ONLY GOT ONE MORE SHOT AT LIFE. #### IT! I FEEL… FINE. MAYBE IT WAS JUST A STUPID MYTH-- #ACK!  #AHHHHH… AHHHH… AHH… #HUFF# IT'S GONE. THE MEMORIES. THE LIVES. I'M ALIVE. THE DREAM OF MY FUTURE MY OWN. NO MORE REINCARNATION. JUST THE LIFE AHEAD OF ME AND WHAT I CHOOSE TO MAKE OF IT. #ACK! ARE YOU KIDDING ME?! THIS IS IT? THIS IS HOW IT ENDS? NOW?! AND NO MORE… NO MORE COMING BACK. THIS IS HOW I DIE? SO WHY DO I FEEL SO ALIVE? #HAH! MY HEART IS BEATING FASTER THAN IT EVER HAS. THIS IS WHAT IT FELT LIKE BEFORE I KNEW ABOUT THE PAST. THIS IS WHAT IT FEELS LIKE TO KNOW THE FUTURE IS YOUR OWN. NOT ONE THAT IS HANDED TO YOU… … BUT ONE THAT YOU FIGHT FOR. THAT'S TRUE LIVING. THAT'S THE DREAM OF MY HEART. #HAHAHAHHAHAHAHAHA! #HAHAHAHHAHAHAHAHA!

full_title_text: I WAS THE DAUGHTER OF THE NURSEMAID. HE WAS THE SON OF THE LORD OF THE HOUSE. CLASS AND WEALTH SEPARATED US. AND YET WE BOTH WERE BOUND TOGETHER BY ONE THING… JOAN, DARLING, PLEASE! CAN'T YOU SEE THAT NOTHING ELSE MATTERS?! NOT MY FATHER! NOT MY POSITION! NOT THIS HOUSE! THE ONLY THING THAT MATTERS --IS YOU! ALL THESE YEARS! IT'S WHAT I'VE ALWAYS WANTED TO HEAR! AND YET I KNOW, EVEN IF HE BELIEVES IT'S TRUE, IT'S ALL A LIE! THIS IS THE ABBEY INTO WHICH I WAS BORN AND IN WHICH I WAS RAISED. HUMBLY KNOWN AS HILL HOUSE, IT SITS ON THOUSANDS OF ACRES AND IS HOME TO GENERATIONS OF NOBILITY, THE LORDS AND LADIES OF WESTSHIRE. THOUGH THIS WAS AND ALWAYS WILL BE MY HOME, I MYSELF WAS NOT OF SUCH HIGH BLOOD. I WAS MERELY, BUT PROUDLY, THE DAUGHTER OF THE NURSEMAID. MY PRETTY LITTLE GIRL, LOOK AT YOU, YOU LOOK JUST LIKE ME MUM. IT'S LIKE LOOKING BACK IN TIME, ISN'T IT? WE'LL HAVE TO CALL YOU JOAN, THEN. DON'T SEE A CHOICE ABOUT IT. MEANWHILE, ON THAT SAME DAY, AT THAT SAME HOUR, JUST A FEW FLOORS BELOW, THE LADY OF WESTSHIRE WELCOMED HER FIRSTBORN, FARE THE HEIR TO THE LAND AND HEARTH. THERE, YOU SEE, A BOY, AS PROMISED. OUR ROGER. THE NEXT ROGER. WHAT A LEGACY YOU INHERIT, CHILD, WHAT A LIFE YOU SHALL LEAD. THE LADY OF THE HOUSE WAS KINDLY, AND SHE ALLOWED MY MOTHER TO CARE FOR ME AS SHE HELPED TO RAISE THE YOUNG LORD ROGER. AND IN THAT CONTEXT, WE TOOK OUR FIRST STEPS TOGETHER. SAID OUR FIRST WORDS TO ONE ANOTHER. WE TAUGHT EACH OTHER HOW TO PLAY. WE TAUGHT EACH OTHER HOW TO LAUGH. AND YES, DESPITE MY MOTHER'S MANY, MANY PROTESTS, WE TAUGHT EACH OTHER TIME AND AGAIN HOW TO FIGHT. AND… HOW TO LOVE! AS FOR OUR FIRST KISS… ROGER! TODAY I AM FOURTEEN YEARS OLD AND TODAY YOU ARE ALSO FOURTEEN YEARS OLD AND SO WE HAVE TO KISS! ROGER! TODAY I AM FOURTEEN YEARS OLD AND TODAY YOU ARE ALSO FOURTEEN YEARS OLD AND SO WE HAVE TO KISS!  ALL RIGHT. WELL… IT WAS SHARED. #HA HA HA HA HA AND IT WAS LOVELY. HOWEVER, AS THE YEARS PASSED, WE LEARNED QUICKLY ENOUGH THAT THOUGH WE WERE BORN IN THE SAME ILLUSTRIOUS MANOR… WE STILL LIVED IN TWO SEPARATE WORLDS. JOAN! HELLO, ROGER. DO YOU LIKE MY NEW OUTFIT? THE BOOTS WERE A GIFT FROM THE KING FOR MY BIRTHDAY. THEY CAME WITH A VERY KIND NOTE WISHING ME WELL. AND TODAY FATHER IS TAKING ME ON MY FIRST HUNT, ISN'T THAT JUST THRILLING, JOAN? OH, IT'S SO WONDERFUL, ROGER! I BET YOU CATCH FORTY PHEASANTS! AT LEAST! I WISH YOU COULD COME, I DO. I AM SO USED TO HAVING YOU BY MY SIDE. NOTHING FEELS QUITE RIGHT WITHOUT YOU. DON'T BE SILLY. ANGELICA IS ILL AND I HAVE TO PREPARE THE CURTAINS IN THE GRAND HALL ON MY OWN. IT WILL TAKE HOURS. NOT THAT… BUT I WOULD LOVE TO ONE DAY, I WOULD LOVE TO LEARN TO SHOOT AS YOU DO. I WOULD LOVE TO… I WOULD LOVE FOR YOU TO TEACH ME. YOU'LL DO THAT, WON'T YOU, ROGER? PLEASE, PLEASE PROMISE ME. AND SO THE DAYS SLIPPED BY, AND WE EACH MET THE OBLIGATIONS ASSIGNED TO US AT BIRTH. ROGER WENT UPON HIS WAY. C'MON, CHESTER, GIVE IT A GO, OLD BOY. GLORY AWAITS. AND I WENT UPON MINE. AREN'T YOU A FILTHY THING? HOW HAVE THEY BEEN TREATING YOU TO GET YOU THIS WAY? YEARS PASSED, AND I WAS GIVEN A PERMANENT POSITION IN THE HOUSE. MY MOTHER TOLD EVERYONE I WAS BLESSED, FATED EVEN, TO BECOME THE HOUSE KEEPER OF HILL HOUSE. IF YOU COULD IMAGINE. ROGER SEEMED TO GROW MORE CONFIDENT (AND MORE DASHING!) EACH DAY. HIS UNTARNISHED REPUTATION AS A MAN OF AMBITION AND FORTITUDE SPREAD ACROSS THE COUNTRYSIDE, AND MANY A GOSSIP WONDERED WHO WOULD BE THE LUCKY LASS TO FINALLY CATCH HIS EYE. SOON THE LADY WAS ARRANGING FOR DOZENS OF GIRLS FROM THE BEST FAMILIES, FROM ALL OVER THE COUNTRY, TO COME TO HILL HOUSE AND MEET MY ROGER. I MEAN, AND MEET HER ROGER. OF COURSE THAT'S WHAT I MEAN. HOW STUPID OF ME. BUT THEN AGAIN… JOAN… ROGER? JOAN, I… I WAS WONDERING… WELL, I'M SORRY TO… BUT… BUT YOU SEE… I REMEMBER I… I DID PROMISE YOU… A WHILE BACK… TOO LONG, REALLY… BUT I SAID… IF YOU… I'VE BEEN THINKING ON IT… WELL, I HAD SOME TIME AND… AND I THOUGHT PERHAPS WE MIGHT… IS EVERYTHING ALL RIGHT, ROGER? YOU LOOK FLUSHED. JOAN, WOULD YOU… COULD YOU… I… I WOULD BE HAPPY IF I MIGHT SHOW YOU HOW TO SHOOT, TAKE YOU NOW, IN FACT. YOU DID SAY YOU WANTED TO LEARN, JOAN. DIDN'T YOU? OH, YES, VERY MUCH. JOLLY! THAT'S… THAT'S JUST JOLLY! ROGER TOOK ME TO A SMALL COTTAGE HALF A MILE FROM THE HOUSE, NEAR THE EDGE OF THE WEST FOREST. THEY KEPT THE SHOTGUNS HERE, HE EXPLAINED POLITELY, AND WE COULD TAKE THEM AND GO TO THE WOODS AND PRACTICE. I WOULD LIKE THAT, ROGER. TO PRACTICE, I MEAN. YES, THAT WOULD BE… HE WAS SUDDENLY SO CLOSE TO ME. I FELT HIS HEART BEAT AS I'M SURE HE FELT MINE. OH JOAN. AND THEN… OH, AND THEN… THEY WERE BEATING AS ONE! WELL? HOW… IF YOU START IN WITH THE LAUGHING, JOAN DARLING, I'M JUST GOING TO ABOUT DIE! NO. NO, NO, NO, MY SWEET, MY OWN, MY ROGER. THAT WAS DIVINE. BUT WEREN'T WE HERE FOR THE SHOOTING? HIS LIPS UPON MINE, I SHOULD'VE FELT SAFE, SECURE, AS IF ALL THE PROBLEMS OF YESTERDAY WERE MERE SOAP BUBBLES, SO EASILY POPPED AS WE REACHED OUR HAPPILY EVER AFTER. BUT INSTEAD I KNEW WE WERE JUST AT THE BEGINNING OF… ROGER! MY SON! MY BOY! HOW COULD YOU SHAME OUR FAMILY LIKE THIS?! HOW COULD YOU BETRAY WHO YOU ARE?! AFTER OUR FIRST --NO, SECOND! --MAGNIFICENT KISS, ROGER AND I WENT BACK TO OUR OWN WORLDS. I CONTINUED TO PREPARE THE HOUSE FOR THE EVENING… AND HE CONTINUED TO PREPARE HIMSELF FOR THE GLORIOUS DESTINY THAT HAD AWAITED HIM SINCE BEFORE HIS BIRTH. WHENEVER WE'D SEE EACH OTHER, IT WAS ALL HANDLED VERY FORMALLY. IF ANYTHING, IT WAS PERHAPS A BIT MORE STIFF AND REHEARSED THAN BEFORE. MISS PETERSON. MY LORD. BUT EVERY FEW DAYS, HE'D COME TO ME AND OFFER ME A " HUNTING LESSON, ” AND WE'D DASH OFF TO THE SMALL COTTAGE WITH ALL THE GUNS. HURRY, DARLING, THE HOURS ARE NOT AS LONG AS THEY SEEM! OH, ROGER, REALLY! AND THERE WE'D FIND OUR SANCTUARY AND WE'D AGAIN SHARE OUR KISSES. YOU KNOW, JOAN, DARLING, WE DON'T HAVE TO GO AHEAD WITH THE FARCE OF THE HIKE AND THE HOUNDS. WE MIGHT SPEND THIS TIME MORE… INTIMATELY. I WISH IT WERE SO SIMPLE, ROGER. BUT IF WE NEVER LEAVE THE INSIDE OF THAT HOUSE, THEN THIS FLIMSY EXCUSE WILL TAKE TO THE WIND FASTER THAN THOSE BIRDS.  NO, EVERYONE THINKS YOU ARE THE KIND GENTLEMAN TEACHING AN OLD, POOR FRIEND A NEW TRICK. AND I'M AFRAID WE MUST DO OUR BEST TO ACT THAT OUT. OR RISK LOSING IT ALTOGETHER! WAS IT NOT A FINE SHOT, ROGER?! I AM GETTING QUITE GOOD, AREN'T I? YES, MY DARLING. QUITE! WEEKS PASSED, THE HAPPIEST WEEKS OF MY LIFE. IT DIDN'T SEEM TO MATTER IN WHAT DRUDGERY I WAS ENGAGED, FOR MY THOUGHTS WERE ALWAYS ON THE HUNT. ON ROGER AND THE HUNT, I MEAN. FOR THE HUNT WAS AN EXCUSE FOR US TO BE TOGETHER WHEN THE STORMS OF CLASS AND WEALTH WERE ALWAYS TRYING TO REND US APART. I MEAN. I NEVER WANTED THOSE DAYS TO END. BUT, SADLY, IF YOU KNOW ANYTHING, YOU KNOW NOTHING IS EVERLASTING. JOAN! I SAW YOU WALKING, I WAS BEHIND YOU, LOOKING AT YOU, AND JOAN, I CANNOT DO IT ANYMORE! I CANNOT LIVE THIS WAY IN MY OWN HOUSE! HIDING LIKE THE PHEASANTS IN THE FIELD! WAITING FOR THE DOGS TO COME!  JOAN DARLING, THE HUNT MUST END! YOU MUST MARRY ME! ROGER! I WAS IN HIS ARMS WHERE I HAD ALWAYS LONGED TO BE, AND IT WAS AGAIN LOVELY, AND YET I COULD FEEL NOTHING BUT FEAR. WE CAN'T, MY LOVE… WE CAN'T… DON'T, JOAN. I KNOW ALL THE POWERS GATHERED AGAINST US. BUT THEY DON'T KNOW MY POWER, THEY CAN'T UNDERSTAND MY STRENGTH. OH, HOW HIS WORDS LIFTED ME, I BEGAN TO FEEL A DASH OF HOPE. MY STRENGTH WHEN I AM WITH YOU. BUT THEN! AT THE DOOR! LORD WESTSHIRE! MY WORD! WHAT IS THIS, ROGER?! GET YOUR HANDS OFF THAT COMMON WOMAN! FATHER! YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND-- I UNDERSTAND PERFECTLY WELL! I WILL NOT HAVE SOME DALLIANCE BECOME A SCANDAL! THIS BEHAVIOR WILL NOT BE TOLERATED IN THIS HOUSE! YOU HAVE DUTIES TO THE NAME I GIFTED YOU, AND I WILL SEE THEM FULFILLED! FATHER, JOAN IS NOT A DALLIANCE! I LOVE HER! YOU YOUNG FOOL! YOU HAVE NO IDEA WHAT LOVE IS! ROGER LEFT AFTER THAT. OR RATHER, HIS PARENTS SENT HIM AWAY TO LIVE WITH SOME COUSIN OR OTHER. I EXPECTED TO BE LET GO, BUT THE FAMILY WAS DESPERATE TO HIDE ANY HINT OF IMPROPRIETY AND TO SQUASH EVERY RUMOR. THE DISMISSAL OF THE MAID AT THE SAME TIME AS ROGER'S DEPARTURE COULD BE THE CAUSE OF A GREAT DEAL OF TALK. AND A GREAT DEAL OF TALK WAS ALWAYS TO BE AVOIDED. SO I RESUMED MY CHORES, CLEANING HILL HOUSE FOR ALL THE GOOD MEN AND WOMEN WHO LIVED THERE. ALL OF THOSE RICH, WELLBORN PEOPLE WHO EXPECTED A WELL-KEPT HOUSE. FOR THEM, I SCRUBBED AND I WASHED AND I FOLDED AND I DUSTED AND I… AND I… AND I HEARD ROGER'S WORDS, AGAIN AND AGAIN. "DARLING,” HE SAID, "THE HUNT MUST END!" MONTHS PASSED AND THEN THE DAY CAME, THE DAY I HAD BEEN WAITING FOR SINCE BEFORE I WAS BORN ON THIS GRAND ESTATE. IT WASN'T MUCH, JUST AN EPISTLE DISCREETLY DELIVERED BY THE MILKMAID, JUST ONE MAGICAL SENTENCE IN THE MIDST OF HIS ORNATE PROCLAMATIONS OF LOVE. " JOAN, DARLING, MEET ME IN OUR PLACE. " AS SOON AS I WAS ABLE, I RUSHED OUT TO THE HUNTING COTTAGE. I COULD NOT BELIEVE IT WAS ALL HAPPENING. I HAD DREAMED THIS MOMENT WOULD COME, BUT DREAMS CAN BE SO FAR FROM WHAT IS REAL! YET THERE IT ALL WAS, ALL LAID OUT FOR ME. JOAN, MY BLOSSOM, FORGIVE ME, WHEN MY FATHER-- I WAS A COWARD, JOAN! I SHOULDN'T HAVE LEFT, BUT I'VE RETURNED! I COULDN'T LIVE WITHOUT YOU! I WILL BE A COWARD NO LONGER! MY CHANCE TO ESCAPE. MARRY ME, JOAN! PLEASE, FORGET ALL THE TROUBLES WE'VE HAD OR WILL HAVE AND JUST REMEMBER YOU AND I-- YOU AND I FROM THE BEGINNING AND TO THE END! MARRY ME, DARLING! MARRY ME! NO.  WHAT?    ROGER, DARLING, PLEASE, I WANT YOU TO LISTEN CLOSELY TO MY WORDS AND KNOW THAT I SINCERELY MEAN THEM.    I HAVE LIED TO YOU SO MANY TIMES, BUT IT IS IMPORTANT THAT YOU KNOW, THAT EVERYONE KNOWS, WHAT I AM ABOUT TO SAY --THIS IS NOT A LIE. JOAN, I DON'T… WHAT? I WILL NEVER MARRY YOU. EVER. THERE IS NOTHING THAT CAN BE DONE TO CHANGE MY MIND, YOU UNDERSTAND THAT? NOTHING. AND I NEVER LOVED YOU, POOR BOY. NEVER. NOT FOR A SINGLE MOMENT. JOAN! YOU… YOU DON'T KNOW WHAT YOU'RE SAYING! I AM SORRY, ROGER, I AM. DEEPLY. AND NOT JUST FOR THE RUSE. BUT ALSO FOR… I'M JUST SO SORRY FOR EVERYTHING THAT… FROM OUTSIDE, I HEAR THE CLICK, THE HAMMER BEING PULLED BACK ON HIS PISTOL. THERE'S SOMETHING WRONG? WHAT IS WRONG WITH YOU? OH ROGER. YOU POOR THING. I AM USED TO IT BY NOW. #GUHH! WITH ROGER BLEEDING BEHIND ME, I COCK THE SHOTGUN AND READY MY NERVES. IT HAS BEEN A LONG, ARDUOUS JOURNEY FROM CHILDHOOD TO HERE, BUT I EXPECTED NOTHING LESS ON… WHAT… WHAT THE BLOODY @%@$ IS GOING ON? SHUT THE FUCK UP, ROGER! YOU'RE ALREADY FUCKING DEAD! LET ME WORRY ABOUT THE LIVING! FOLLOW THE PATTERN. TEN TIMES OUT OF TEN, HE HITS ME ON THE FIRST SHOT. AND IF I DON'T DIE RIGHT AWAY, HE CHECKS THE KILL AND SHOOTS AGAIN. JUST WAIT. HAVE PATIENCE. JOAN… I… I… AM HURT… HE'S COMING. ROGER! WHAT IS YOUR PROBLEM? SHUT THE FUCK UP. SERIOUSLY. HE'S COMING. THE COWBOY'S HERE. JOAN, DARLING… TELL MOTHER… TELL HER I LOVED… I'M USED TO THE KICKBACK. FUCK YOU! I KNOW I HAVE A SECOND SHOT. YOU HEAR, COWBOY?! GO FUCK YOURSELF! I KNOW HOW TO LOAD IT. YOU CAN FEEL WHAT IT'S LIKE TO BE FUCKING SHOT FOR ONCE! YOU WAKE UP SOME OTHER FUCKING PLACE, SOME OTHER FUCKING TIME! THANKS TO ROGER. I CAN'T DIE, JOAN… I'M… I'M THE HEIR… THEY DEPEND ON… THE WHOLE VILLAGE… DEPENDS… JOAN… I'M SO… WET… GOOD AND KIND ROGER. THAT'S ENOUGH. IF YOU DON'T SHUT YOUR FUCKING MOUTH, ROGER, I'M GOING TO USE THIS GUN TO BLOW YOUR HEAD OFF YOUR BLOODY-- HE SHOULD BE DEAD. THE COWBOY'S DEAD. I DID IT. AFTER ALL THESE LIVES. AND STILL, THE BULLETS RIP THROUGH ME. NO! #NNNNN… JOAN! JOAN? D-DARLING JOAN? AH, HELL. HOWDY. WHO'S HE? I… I… SIR, I… I AM ROGER HENRY CHARLES ANGSTROM… THE… FUTURE… ELEVENTH LORD OF WEST… WESTSHIRE… WHO… PLEASURE TO MEET YOU, ROGER. ANY FRIEND OF JOAN'S IS A FRIEND OF MINE. HELL OF A GIRL, THAT JOANIE, AIN'T SHE? SHE GROWS ON YOU FAST, I'LL SAY THAT. WHAT… I DON'T… WHAT? GIVE ME A SECOND HERE, ROGER, WON'T YOU? I GOT A MESSAGE I GOT TO DELIVER TO JOAN, I DOUBT SHE'LL HEAR IT IN HER STATE, BUT I GAVE MY WORD TO A GOOD WOMAN AND I MEAN TO KEEP IT. JOAN, YOU REMEMBER, DON'T YOU? LOVE IS-- JOAN! MY DARLING! ROGER, NOW WHAT IN ALL TARNATION ARE YOU DOING THERE? IF YOU SCREAM LIKE THAT, ALL LOUD LIKE, YOU THINK JOAN'S GOING TO HEAR A DAMN THING I HAVE TO SAY? THIS IS IMPORTANT, BOY, KEEP YOUR LIPS TIED. full_title_text: Aldus Trask was never really a doctor, not in the way you'd think… … but he fancied himself an excellent chef with the rarest of tastes. For a good minute, the whole family would bring in homeless people. Feed them, groom them, and then hunt them on the Trask Mansion's grounds for sport. And who could forget Maria Trask? SO A LOT OF PEOPLE HAVE DIED IN THE TRASK MANSION… HORRIBLY, WE GET IT. DOESN'T MEAN GHOSTS LIVE THERE, TRICK. OR THAT THEY'RE EVEN REAL. THIS LITTLE HISTORY LESSON ISN'T FOR SHOW AND TELL, KING. YOU NEED TO KNOW THIS. TRICK'S RIGHT. IF WE HAVE ANY CHANCE OF STEALING A GHOST FROM THE TRASK MANSION, WE NEED TO KNOW THE LOWDOWN ON THE WHO'S WHO. ABOUT GODDAMN TIME, JACKSON. I ALREADY TOLD YOU, GHOST HUNTING ISN'T REALLY MY THING. WHAT IS YOUR THING EXACTLY? DISPROVING CON JOBS LIKE YOU, SWEETHEART. I SHOULDN'T BE HERE-- KING. SHUT THE FUCK UP. HERE IS YOUR DOWN PAYMENT. NOW LISTEN UP… YOU CAN TAKE IT OR LEAVE IT. I DON'T CARE. YOUR CHOICE, FRIEND. Of course they took the money. Wouldn't you? OKAY, PEOPLE, YOU'VE GOT ABOUT AN HOUR LEFT BEFORE SUNDOWN. THEN WE'RE OFF LIKE A PROM DRESS AFTER ONE TOO MANY. Thankfully Markus Schrecken is footing the bill for this little smash and grab. His girl, Anderson, is my muscle, and if by some weird ass chance I need someone to fight back bloodthirsty zombies, I know she could handle it. THIS IS A WASTE OF TIME. King is probably trying to refute everything he's heard about the place. I like that. Every team needs their very own devil's advocate. Keeps us on our toes. I KNEW IT. Not sure how much I believe Rusnak's rap. If she's a grade-A con artist or the real deal. Markus swears that if if anyone is going to feel the presence of a ghost in this house, it'll be her. SPEAK TO ME… Jay and Joe Burns think they're using me. This is just an opportunity to film an episode of their TV show and maybe catch a glimpse of a monster. Really, I don't give a shit what they do. I just want their tech. WE'LL PUT A CAMERA THERE AND… THERE. And then we have Robby Trick. Robby Trick is here for the money. Plain and simple. But not just my money. If he can steal something from this place and flip it on the market, he will. I just hope he remembers to keeps his eye on the prize first. WELL, WELL, WELL… NOT BAD. MINE. ARE THE RUMORS TRUE…? BINGO. NOW WHAT COULD THEY BE TRYING TO HIDE, I WONDER? #UNH. OH MY-- NO FUCKING WAY. JACKSON! WHAT ARE YOU AFRAID OF, JACKSON? NOTHING. YOU? NOTHING. OH C'MON, THERE HAS TO BE SOMETHING. SO IT'S OKAY FOR YOU TO BE FEARLESS AND NOT ME? WELL… I MEAN… YOU'RE A GIRL. I REALLY HATE YOU. DID YOU FIND ANYTHING USEFUL? OUR INSTRUMENTS DETECTED SOME INTERESTING ENERGY PATTERNS IN THE WALLS-- WHICH COULD EASILY BE EXPLAINED BY THE FAULTY WIRING I FOUND. HOW ABOUT YOU, DOLL? STILL ZERO. IT'S MY BELIEF THAT I'LL HAVE BETTER LUCK IF I WAS HERE AT NIGHT… NUH-HUH, NO WAY, EMO GIRL. WE'RE NOT COMING AT NIGHT UNLESS IT'S OUR VERY LAST-- JACKSON… YOU WON'T BELIEVE WHAT I JUST UNEARTHED IN THE MASTER LIBRARY. THIS BETTER BE GOOD, TRICK. IT'S GONNA HAVE TO WAIT… WE GOT TROUBLE. SHIT. BURNS BOYS… TAKE CARE OF IT. GOOD EVENING, OFFICER… WHAT CAN WE DO YOU FOR? HEY, I KNOW YOU! YOU'RE THOSE GHOST TRAPPERS, YEAH?! FROM TV?! YOU'RE GOING TO MAKE US BLUSH. YOU MAKING AN EPISODE OR WHATEVER? YOU KNOW THIS PLACE HAS GOTS SOME MEAN HISTORY, YEAH? YOU GOT US. WE'RE SCOUTING TO SEE IF WE LIKE THE LOCATION. SINCE YOU'RE A FAN, YOU KNOW HOW MUCH WE LIKE TO KEEP A LOW PROFILE. DID WE DO SOMETHING WRONG? SOMEONE CALLED IN THE CARS PARKED OUT FRONT, SO I HAD TO COME DO A LOOKSY. THERE ARE NIGHTS WE GET PEOPLE COMING UP HERE FOR NO GOOD. KIDS THESE DAYS, Y'KNOW? IN THAT CASE, WE'LL BE SURE NOT TO CAUSE ANY TROUBLE. AH, SHOOT, YOU BOYS ARE ALRIGHT BY ME. IF YA NEED ANYTHING, GIMME A HOLLER. HE'S GONE. THAT COULD BE A PROBLEM LATER, HUH? YEAH… MAYBE… FUCK. TRICK? SOMETHING YOU WANTED TO SHOW ME? NO…. UM… NOT REALLY. IT CAN WAIT. YOU BETTER NOT BE TRYING TO POCKET- SUN IS SETTING. TIME TO BOUNCE. EVERYONE GRAB YOUR SHIT AND LET'S GO. HUSTLE, PEOPLE. THIS IS A JOKE. WHY DO I EVEN BOTHER? OH YEAH… MONEY… KING! MOVE IT OR LOSE IT, BUDDY! I'M COMING! I DON'T SEE WHAT THE BIG DEAL IS… THERE ARE NO SUCH THINGS AS… … GHOSTS. YOU KNOW HOW ABSOLUTELY RIDICULOUS THIS IS, JACKSON? DOESN'T MATTER. THE GIG IS THE GIG. AND THE LAST TIME I DIDN'T RESPECT THE GIG… PEOPLE DIED… SO… FIRST THING TOMORROW WE DO THE SAME THING. AND OUT AGAIN BY SUNDOWN. CAPICE? WE'LL BE HERE WITH OUR CREW FIRST THING IN THE MORNING. WE WANT TO START FILMING. JUST REMEMBER OUR DEAL. NOTHING AIMED AT ME OR I BREAK A LENS. TRICK? SINCE WE CAN'T GO IN AT NIGHT, I NEED YOU TO PROCURE A FEW THINGS FOR ME. THEY WILL HELP ME SENSE GHOSTS DURING THE DAYLIGHT HOURS. OKAY, EASY, EASY, EASY. OH… WAIT, WAIT… THIS LAST ONE IS GOING TO BE HARD. YOU'VE GOT TWELVE HOURS. YOU'RE KIDDING? YOU'RE NOT KIDDING. WELL, I HATE TO BREAK IT TO YOU… BUT I ONLY KNOW ONE PERSON WHO HAS IT… "YOUR BOSS. "MARKUS SCHRECKEN. " YOU THINK HE'LL LET US TAKE IT FROM HIS PRECIOUS COLLECTION? NOT A CHANCE IN HELL. THEN WE'LL HAVE TO STEAL IT. #AH! #GAK! #NWWW. JACKSON? I CONVINCED THE COP TO NOT BOTHER US. CASH DID THE JOB. SEE YOU AT SCHRECKEN'S IN AN HOUR. DON'T BE LATE.

full_title_text: Something I'm often accused of is using people. As if that's some kind of insult. Building the best team for a score is a talent. Each member is a tool for the job. The killer. The thief. The skeptic. And then the believer. Cogs in my machine. But today… WAIT, WAIT… WE CAN HELP YOU. HELP YOU BE FREE. The ghosts in the machine are out to ruin my job. I DON'T THINK THEY'RE BUYING WHAT YOU'RE SELLING, RUSNAK! RUN! WE ARE SO FUCKED! #HHSSS SHIT! DIDN'T EVEN FAZE HIM! SPEAK FOR YOURSELF, KING! THEY HATE SUNLIGHT, YEAH? THEN MAYBE A LITTLE HEAT WILL DO THE JOB. STICK TO THE PLAN! GET TRICK TO SAFETY AND THEN-- THERE IS NO PLAN, JACKSON. WE HAVE THE GHOST WE CAME FOR. GAME OVER. OH, IT'S NOT A PARTY UNLESS A GUN IS AIMED AT SOMEONE'S HEAD, IS IT NOW, JACKSON? HOW ARE YOU GOING TO GET THE GHOST OUT OF HIM, ANDERSON?! #HUNH?! NOT MY CONCERN. AND THE REST OF YOU CAN JUST DIE HERE AS FAR AS I'M-- DAMN! KNEW YOU WERE MARKUS'S PET BITCH FROM THE BEGINNING, ANDERSON. IT'S BEEN FUN, KIDS, BUT I'M TAKING THIS BODY FOR A RIDE! OH NO, YOU DON'T! JACKSON, WE CAME HERE TO DO A JOB. AND I'M GOING TO FINISH IT WITH OR WITHOUT YOU. YOU HAVE A CHOICE. YOU DON'T HAVE TO DO THIS! WE DON'T HAVE TO GIVE MARKUS ANYTHING. YOU'LL NEVER ESCAPE THIS HOUSE, KING! IT LOVES ITS GUESTS TOO MUCH. MARKUS IS GOING TO GET HIS GHOST! MAYBE THE HOUSE WILL LET ME TRADE. THEY GIVE ME AN OLD GHOST, AND I'LL GIVE THEM A… NEW ONE! JACKSON! I'M BEGINNING TO LIKE THIS GIRL. THE ACT IS OVER, JACKSON. YOU CAN DITCH THE WHOLE " HAUNTED, COOL GUY " ROUTINE NOW. JUST FOCUS ON DYING, OKAY? WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS? WHY DO YOU FOLLOW MARKUS'S ORDERS SO BLINDLY? WHAT DOES THAT OLD FART GOT ON YOU? HE SAVED ME! MARKUS STOLE ME AWAY FROM SEX TRADERS ON THE BULGARIAN BORDER. IF IT WASN'T FOR MARKUS, I WOULD HAVE HAD A LIFETIME OF SLAVERY. SO YOU TRADED ONE LIFETIME OF SLAVERY FOR ANOTHER. HARDLY. MARKUS ALWAYS TOOK AMAZING CARE OF ME. SAID I REMINDED HIM OF HIS LOST LITTLE SISTER. YOU LOOK NOTHING LIKE HER. HOW WOULD YOU KNOW? CALL IT A HUNCH. WHAT IS THAT SUPPOSED TO MEAN?! IF WE'RE EVER GOING TO GET OUT OF THIS, YOU'LL NEED TO TALK TO THESE SPIRITS. I THOUGHT YOU DIDN'T BELIEVE? ONLY YOU NEED TO BELIEVE!  I DON'T KNOW WHAT I BELIEVE ANYMORE, BUT THAT DOESN'T MATTER! SPIRITS… REVEAL YOURSELVES TO ME. LET ME… SEE! " MARKUS SEARCHED THE WORLD FOR ARTIFACTS THAT COULD HELP HIM REMAIN YOUNG AND RICH, UNTIL ONE DAY HE FIGURED IT OUT. A RITUAL THAT CURSED THE TRASK MANSION… " BUT COST HIM HIS SISTER'S LIFE. " AS LONG AS THE TRASK MANSION WAS HAUNTED… " MARKUS WOULD BE IMMORTAL. " WHEN HE FOUND OUT THAT THE MANSION WAS GOING TO BE TOTALED, HE NEEDED TO RETRIEVE ONE OF THE GHOSTS TO KEEP THE CURSE WORKING. " MAN, THAT SONOFABITCH. THIS WAS NEVER ABOUT ADDING TO HIS COLLECTION. IT'S JUST HIS SICK DESIRE TO LIVE FOREVER. HEY, JACKSON… WE'RE SCREWED, BUDDY! YOU GOT A PLAN?! I'M WORKING ON IT. YOU THINK YOUR CUTE LITTLE ONE-LINERS ARE GOING TO GET YOU OUT OF THIS, JACKSON?! TELL ME WHAT YOU'RE AFRAID OF… IT WAS MY TEAM… " MY CREW THOUGHT WE WERE REAL HOT SHIT. OUT TO ROB A BRAND NEW CASINO FOR OUR BIGGEST SCORE EVER. " HOW WERE WE SUPPOSED TO KNOW THAT PLACE WAS ON TOP OF SOME OLD ASS INDIAN BURIAL GROUND? " MY WHOLE TEAM GOT POSSESSED. " EVERYONE… DIED. " BUT THAT IS NOT YOUR REAL SECRET, WINTERS. THE ONE THAT REALLY HAUNTS YOU. YOU NEED TO LET GO OF YOUR GUILT. ONLY THEN WILL YOU BE ABLE TO DEFEAT THIS CURSED HOUSE. WHAT IF I MADE YOU A COUNTER OFFER? I HAVE… A PLAN. WHO ARE YOU TALKING TO, DAMMIT?! SO CLOSE TO DEATH THAT YOU'RE STARTING TO SEE THINGS? YOU ALWAYS THIS CLUELESS? WHY DON'T YOU JUST GO AHEAD AND PUT THE KNIFE AWAY AND WE CAN ALL WALK OUT OF HERE ALIVE? SUCH A SCREW UP. I KNOW ALL ABOUT YOU AND YOUR THING WITH KNIVES AND YOUR LAST TEAM. LEAVING YOU WITH SOME KIND OF WEAK-ASS SURVIVOR GUILT. AND NOW YOUR WHOLE TEAM IS GETTING RIPPED APART BY GHOSTS AGAIN. ALL YOU HAD TO DO WAS STEAL ONE GHOST AND YOU COULDN'T EVEN DO THAT RIGHT! THE PLAN WAS NEVER TO STEAL JUST ONE GHOST… WHAT? IF YOU ROB A BANK YOU DON'T TAKE JUST THE HUNDREDS. YOU TAKE ALL OF IT. WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT? " RUSNAK WAS LOYAL TO MARKUS AND PLANNED TO BETRAY US FROM THE VERY BEGINNING. YOU THINK I EVER TRUSTED HER FOR A SECOND? OF COURSE NOT. BUT I OFFERED HER A BETTER DEAL. " MORE MONEY. " SO, HONEY… HE'S SAYING YOU'RE SCREWED. I'M GOING TO NEED YOU TO MOVE THAT ASS, JACKSON! POSSESS  HER!    YES, MA'AM! DAMMIT, RUSNAK! THAT ALL YOU CARE ABOUT?! MONEY?! WHAT ABOUT LOYALTY?! NO! I LIKE THIS BODY! WHOA! WE MADE A PACT WITH THE OLDEST GHOST IN THE HOUSE, ANDERSON. THESE GHOSTS WANT REVENGE ON MARKUS. AND WE HAVE NO PROBLEM HELPING THEM! NO… NO… YOU CAN'T CONTROL THEM! NO! #EEEIIIIII!!! DON'T WORRY. THE CURSE STARTED WITH ME. CONTROL WILL BE -- MINE. WE ARE ALL… TRAPPED IN THIS BODY… FOR NOW. UM… WHAT THE HELL JUST HAPPENED?! RUSNAK… SAVED THE DAY. THIS MUMBO JUMBO ACTUALLY WORKED. I UM, THINK I NEED TO SIT DOWN. KING… YOU KNOW IT WASN'T JUST THAT. YOUR IDEA MIXED WITH JACKSON'S ORIGINAL PLAN IS WHAT DID IT. IS THAT WHY YOU DIDN'T TELL ANDERSON THE WHOLE PLAN OF STEALING ALL THE GHOSTS? YOU KNEW SHE'D TRY TO SCREW US? YUP. ARE WE REALLY GIVING MARKUS THIS… GHOST BOMB? OF COURSE WE ARE. AFTER WE GET PAID… SORRY. WE NEEDED TO BORROW IT. BUT TRUST ME WHEN I SAY IT CAME IN HANDY. YOU THINK WALKING OUT OF THE SHADOWS WILL INTIMIDATE ME, WINTERS? JUST ANOTHER WASTE OF MY TIME. HAVE SOME FAITH, MARKUS. I HAVE WHAT YOU WANTED… YOUR GHOST. GIFT WRAPPED IN A TALL BLONDE. POSSESSION? HOW RUTHLESS OF YOU. RUTHLESS AND BRILLIANT. KNEW YOU WERE THE RIGHT MAN FOR THE JOB. WELL… A DEAL IS A DEAL. SAY NO MORE, MISTER WINTERS. I'M A MAN OF MY WORD. THE CASH WE AGREED ON AND ALL YOU'LL NEED TO TAKE OVER MY PRIVATE RESORT. YOURS. MUST FEEL NICE TO HAVE SOME KIND OF REDEMPTION AFTER YOUR LAST JOB WAS SUCH A DISASTER. WHO EVER SAID I WANTED REDEMPTION? WELL, I JUST ASSUMED THAT-- AND THERE YOU GO AGAIN… IF YOU KNEW ANYTHING ABOUT THE OLD ME, IT'S THAT I USED TO NOT GIVE TWO SHITS ABOUT PEOPLE. AND ESPECIALLY THE PEOPLE I USED. THAT LAST GIG WAS THE SCORE OF A LIFETIME, BUT YOU KNOW WHAT? THERE WAS NO WAY I COULD HAVE PREDICTED THAT JOINT BEING HAUNTED, SO THAT ISN'T WHY I'M ALL BROKEN UP INSIDE. MY WHOLE TEAM WAS POSSESSED AND BACK THEN… " I DIDN'T CARE. " I'M A SURVIVOR. I WAS GOING TO DO WHATEVER I NEEDED TO DO. RIGHT OR WRONG… DIDN'T MATTER. I'M STILL ALIVE. AND THEY'RE NOT. " THAT'S WHY I'M HAUNTED. AND NOTHING WILL EVER CHANGE THAT. BUT I'LL BE DAMNED IF I COULDN'T SAVE SOME OF MY TEAM THIS TIME… AND SOMEONE ELSE. IT'S LOVELY YOU'RE SO SELF-AWARE. BUT JUST LIKE YOU… I DON'T CARE. NOW EXORCISE MY DEAR ANDERSON AND GET MY GHOST OUT. OH, THAT'S NOT MY PROBLEM ANYMORE. SHE'S ALL YOURS. YOU CHEAT! IF YOU DON'T GET BACK HERE AND FINISH THE JOB YOU'LL… PAY… YOU'RE THE ONE WHO NEEDS TO PAY. WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?! DON'T JUST LET HIM WALK AWAY! GO AFTER HIM! NO, BROTHER! YOU CURSED OUR FAMILY, AND OUR HOME, AND IT'S TIME FOR YOU TO FEEL THE PAIN YOU HAVE INFLICTED UPON OTHERS. BROT-- ABIGAIL? YOU'RE THE GHOST THEY-- I NEVER THOUGHT THEY'D EVER-- NO. NO, NO, NO. I FORGIVE YOU. BUT THIS IS THE ONLY WAY. ANDERSON?! THIS ISN'T OVER… ABIGAIL… HOW? YOU'RE NOT THE ONLY ONE WHO CAN MAKE A DEAL, MARKUS. JACKSON MADE ME AN OFFER I COULDN'T REFUSE. " HE CAN'T BE SEDUCED BY GHOSTS, UNLIKE YOU. " HE'S SEEN IT GO WRONG IN WAYS THAT YOU BLATANTLY IGNORE. " DOESN'T MATTER, MY DEAR SISTER! YOU TRAPPED IN MY HOME CONTINUES THE CURSE! I'LL STILL LIVE FOREVER! OH, YOU MISUNDERSTAND, BROTHER. MY REVENGE SETS ME FREE, BUT I BROUGHT ALONG A FEW FRIENDS WITH ME… THEY CAN'T STOP YOUR IMMORTALITY, BUT YOU CAN STILL BE… HAUNTED. #AAAHHHH!!! BOOM. Life has a funny way of working out sometimes… The Trask Mansion was destroyed just like Markus said it would be. At least that was one thing he wasn't LYING about. LEAVE IT. For some, the truth can be deadlier than lies. Others finally see what they want to see, and use it. @TODAY WE TALK TO WOMEN WHO CLAIM THE DEVIL IS THE FATHER OF THEIR BABIES! @YOU'LL BE SHOCKED WHEN WE GET THE RESULTS! For some… nothing changes. And then there was me. I do what has to be done. I'll always be dealing with it. Sometimes we have to live with the fact that we're all haunted in some way, but then… You get used to it.

full_title_text: YOU'RE NEXT, SUPERSTAR! You get used to it.   The outside is really no different than being inside. Need to watch your back… And find ways to keep yourself busy. Books take up. most of my time. Only problem is that a lot of the books' pages have been ripped out to pass notes or roll joints. Not knowing how Harry Potter ends isn't what bugs me… It's never stealing a kiss. Going to the movies. Road trips. So many things I took for granted. But really, the worst part is… The food. Three squares of ass. Not quite the same as eating caviar off a supermodel's tits. The only thing that gets me through this is the reminder… … that someday… I'm going to die. #AHHH! STOP! OH DAMN, SON. YOU HEAR THAT? MUST BE A RIOT. NAH NAH, WINTERS, THAT'S MY HOMIES COME TO BUST ME OUT. NO, NO, PLEASE GOD, NO… WHOA, WHOA! JACKSON T. WINTERS… IT'S YOUR LUCKY DAY. ALMOST. CAN YOU BEHAVE, WINTERS? #HM HM. DON'T TRY ANYTHING FUNNY. THE PRISON RIOT IS STILL WELL UNDERWAY, AND IT'LL BE SOME TIME BEFORE THEY EVEN KNOW YOU'RE GONE. YOUR VOICE… SAME BROAD FROM THE PRISON? MY NAME IS ANDERSON LAKE. ANDERSON, HUNH? ANY OF YOUR FRIENDS EVER CALL YOU ANDY? ONLY THE DEAD ONES. WHERE THE HELL ARE WE? THIS IS THE COLLECTION ROOM OF MARKUS SCHRECKEN. THAT'S A MOUTHFUL. MISTER SCHRECKEN HIRED ME TO… RETRIEVE YOU. YOU MIND PUTTING THE BLADE AWAY? I'VE GOT A THING. OF COURSE YOU DO. SO WHAT DOES RICHIE RICH WANT WITH LITTLE OLD ME? I WANT YOU TO STEAL A GHOST. COME AGAIN? AS YOU CAN SEE I HAVE A REASONABLY EXTRAORDINARY COLLECTION OF SUPERNATURAL ARTIFACTS, AND YET IT'S MISSING… A KEY PIECE. SOMETHING THAT WOULD MAKE THE REST LOOK LIKE PETTY KNICK-KNACKS. I'M NOT HEARING ANYTHING THAT RELATES TO ME, MARKUS. ARE YOU FAMILIAR WITH THE TRASK MANSION? THE HOME OF THE FAMOUS TRASK-- YEAH, YEAH, I KNOW THE SCORE. FROM THE VERY BEGINNING THE TRASK FAMILY HAS BEEN INVOLVED IN THE OCCULT AND MYSTICAL… THE TRASK MANSION SCREAMS HAUNTED AND-- MARKUS, COULD YOU SPEED THIS UP AND GET TO THE " BUT. " ##SIGH.# BUT IN TWO WEEKS TIME IT'S SCHEDULED TO BE DESTROYED, SOME SORT OF MINI-MALL OR PUBLIC PARK OR SOME OTHER RUBBISH. I WANT YOU TO FIND OUT IF IT'S TRULY HAUNTED AND BRING BACK A REAL GHOST FOR MY COLLECTION. IT'S AS SIMPLE AS THAT. RIGHT. YOU FAKED A RIOT TO BREAK ME OUT… SO I CAN STEAL CASPER? LET ME ASK YOU THIS REAL QUICK… ARE YOU INSANE? THAT'S DEBATABLE. AT LEAST YOU'RE HONEST. WHY NOT JUST HAVE LITTLE MISS HOMEWRECKER OVER HERE DO THE JOB? OH COME NOW, GIVE YOURSELF MORE CREDIT. BEFORE YOUR INCARCERATION YOU WERE THE BEST AT THIS SORT OF THING. AN ARTIST. IF YOU KNOW AS MUCH ABOUT ME AS YOU CLAIM, THEN YOU KNOW THAT'S NOT ME ANYMORE. RETIRED FOR NEARLY FIFTEEN YEARS. AFTER YOUR TEAM TRIED TO STEAL FROM THAT CASINO, I KNOW. IT WAS… "TRAGIC." THAT'S ONE WAY TO PUT IT. ALL MY FRIENDS DEAD. YES, WELL… GET ME MY GHOST AND I'LL MAKE SURE THAT YOU'RE SAFE ON MY PRIVATE ISLAND WITH ALL THE MONEY YOU'D EVER NEED. FOREVER. WHAT IF I SAY NO? ANDERSON WILL RETURN YOU TO PRISON. LIKE NOTHING EVER HAPPENED. #HM. I'M NOT GOING BACK. THEN WE'RE IN AGREEMENT? WHATEVER. BUT JUST ONE OTHER THING FIRST… YOU FEEL THAT?! IT'S PAIN! THAT'S ALL THERE IS! PAIN THEN DEATH! THOMAS IS SINGING REO SPEEDWAGON'S " CAN'T FIGHT THIS FEELING. " THAT MEAN ANYTHING TO YOU? THAT'S OUR SONG! THANK YOU, THANK YOU. WHAT A LOAD. MAYBE YOU SHOULD LET ME DO THE TALKING. I CAN STILL GET THE JOB DONE, ANDERSON. EVERYONE SAYS YOU'RE THE BEST. IF THAT'S TRUE, THERE IS NO POINT IN LYING TO YOU. I'M NOT A HUNDRED PERCENT ON BOARD WITH THIS MUMBO JUMBO AND- BEFORE YOU CAN STEAL A GHOST FROM THE TRASK MANSION YOU NEED TO MAKE SURE THAT THERE ARE SOME THERE. HOW DID YOU…? GUESS I'M YOUR GIRL. NOBODY'S SHOWING, WINTERS. MAYBE THEY DIDN'T LIKE YOUR PLAN. LOOKS LIKE OUR NEXT STOP WILL BE BACK TO THE PRISON. Y'KNOW, EVERY TIME YOU OPEN YOUR MOUTH… I GET AN ERECTION. THAT'S WHAT I THOUGHT. EVERYONE GETS A COPY, SO NO EXCUSES IF YOU GET LOST. DON'T BE STUPID. I'LL GIVE THIS A QUICK ONCE-OVER. OLD MANSIONS LIKE THIS ARE ALWAYS FULL OF SURPRISES. HEY, SO I HAVE A PRETTY PERTINENT QUESTION… HOW EXACTLY ARE WE SUPPOSED TO STEAL A GHOST? YOU'RE THE EXPERTS, YOU FIGURE IT OUT. BUT, NOW THAT YOU MENTION IT… YOU. PSYCHIC. YOU'RE SUPPOSED TO SEE DEAD PEOPLE, YEAH? EARN YOUR PAY. YES, SIR. #HM… … LET'S SEE. ANYTHING? NO. NOTHING YET.

full_title_text: THEY SAY THERE ARE NO SMALL ROLES. ONLY SMALL ACTORS. THAT WAS ME. A SMALL ACTRESS, WHO HATED THE ROLES AVAILABLE TO HER. SO NOW I MAKE MY OWN ROLES. I MAKE MY OWN RULES, TOO. ROLE OF A LIFETIME. THE TEVINTER CITY OF VENTUS. ALSO OFTEN REFERRED TO BY ITS PREVIOUS NAME, QARINUS. APPARENTLY THE CITY LIKES HAVING MULTIPLE PERSONAS. DEFINITELY A PLACE FOR SOMEONE LIKE ME. RUMOR HAS IT THAT THE QUNARI HAVE THEIR EYES ON THIS CITY. SOME SAY WAR IS IMMINENT. THAT THE CITY WILL FALL. SO THE PEOPLE OF VENTUS ARE DESPERATE. THEY NEED TO LEAVE, AND FAST. THE LAST THING THEY NEED IS TO DEAL WITH AN INQUISITIVE MAGISTER. THIS IS THE ROLE I'LL BE PLAYING IN TODAY'S PERFORMANCE. THERE'S A MAGISTER IN VENTUS NAMED QINTARA. HE HASN'T BEEN SEEN IN YEARS. BUT THEY SAY HE PRACTICES SOME DARK MAGICS. HIS SON JUST EMERGED FROM THE FAMILY ESTATE. YOUNG THING, LOCKED IN THAT ESTATE FOR SO LONG? HIGHLY UNLIKELY HE'LL KNOW HOW TO DEAL WITH A MAGISTER LOOKING INTO RUMORS THAT HIS FAMILY WAS VENATORI, COLLABORATING WITH THE ELDER ONE TO TAKE OVER THE WORLD. THE ROOKIE PLAY WOULD BE TO HEAD STRAIGHT INTO A MEETING WITH THE YOUNG MAN. BUT WHEN PLAYING A ROLE LIKE THIS, YOU WANT THE REST OF THE WORLD TO SELL YOU IN THE PART. LET A FEW OF VENTUS'S MOST INFLUENTIAL AND CHATTY RESIDENTS KNOW I'M HERE. HINT AT WHY. BY THE TIME I APPROACH THE YOUNG MAN, HE'LL BE TERRIFIED. THIS ONE'S NOT TO BE TRIFLED WITH. HE SEEMS THE KIND OF MAN WHO WOULD SEE THROUGH ME IN AN INSTANT. DON'T YOU HAVE A MAN FROM TEVINTER WHO CAN HANDLE THIS SORT OF THING? ADDITIONALLY, IT IS A GOOD RULE IN THIS LINE OF WORK TO NEVER DEAL WITH ANYONE WHO HAS MORE SECRETS THAN YOU DO. HE'S A WANTED MAN. WE CAN'T TAKE THAT RISK. WE'RE RUNNING OUT OF TIME. THIS WHOLE TOWN IS. ALTHOUGH, NOW I'M CURIOUS. WHICH IS ALSO SOMETHING TO AVOID. MUCH LIKE RUNNING INTO FORMER MARKS. OR GETTING YOUR FEELINGS MIXED UP IN YOUR BUSINESS. HE SHOULD NOT BE HERE. HE'S SUPPOSED TO BE IN FERELDEN. I SHOULD JUST LEAVE… … OR PERHAPS I'LL JUST WORK QUICKLY. PARDON ME. ARE YOU CALIX QINTARA? I AM. AND YOU ARE…? MAGISTER ARAMIS. HAVE YOU HEARD OF ME? OF COURSE. YOUR MERCY IS KNOWN ACROSS ALL OF TEVINTER. MY… MERCY? PLEASE, DEAR MAGISTER. WE ALL KNOW THAT VENTUS IS SOON TO FALL. AND MY FATHER, HE IS ILL. OUR FAMILY'S HOLDINGS, OUR LIBRARY, EVERYTHING OF VALUE… WE WILL NOT BE ABLE TO GET IT OUT OF THE CITY BEFORE THE QUNARI ATTACK. IF SOMEONE OF YOUR MERCY AND GENEROSITY WOULD ASSIST IN TRANSPORTING THESE ITEMS, THEN WHEN WE REACH SAFETY-- … YOU'LL LIQUIDATE THE HOLDINGS AND REPAY ME A HUNDRED FOLD. HEY! CUT THE ACT, CHILD. YOU ARE NO QINTARA. I BEG YOUR PARDON? YOU ARE A CON ARTIST. A GRIFTER. I KNOW THE SCAM YOU'RE PLAYING. " THE CHASIND PRINCE, " IT'S OFTEN CALLED. BUT I AM NOT CHASIND. YOU'RE NOT A SMART PERSON, ARE YOU? THEN I SHALL BE BLUNT. YOU ARE, EITHER BY CHOICE OR HAPPENSTANCE, A LIAR WITH NO CONNECTION TO THE RECLUSIVE HOUSE OF QINTARA. I KNOW NOTHING OF THIS CHASIND PRINCE. BUT IF YOU KNOW THAT CON BY NAME, THEN I SUSPECT YOU ARE NOT A MAGISTER. LET'S JUST SKIP THE FANCY TALK, SISTER. NEITHER OF US AIN'T WHAT WE PRETEND TO BE. YOU EXPOSE ME, I EXPOSE YOU. THAT " FANCY TALK " IS NOT A ROLE I PLAY, YOUNG MAN. IT'S CALLED CLASS. CLEARLY, YOU HAVE NONE. HOWEVER, YOU ARE NOT A COMPLETE IMBECILE. SO WE APPEAR TO BE AT A STALEMATE. I DON'T SEE THE PROBLEM. I KEEP DOING WHAT I DO, GET SOME MONEY TO SKIP THIS TOWN BEFORE THE QUNARI INVADE… … AND YOU DO WHATEVER THE HELL YOU CAME TO TOWN TO DO. THAT'S NOT POSSIBLE, AS I CAME HERE TO DO YOU. ER… PERSUADE YOU THAT I WAS A MAGISTER AND WORK THE SITUATION TO A BRIBE. I SPENT THE DAY SPREADING WORD THAT HOUSE QINTARA WAS UNDER INVESTIGATION. I CAN SHIFT TARGETS EASILY ENOUGH. BUT I AM NOW LINKED TO YOU. SO, MAYBE WE CAN WORK TOGETHER. NO. NOT AN OPTION, AS YOU ARE AN AMATEUR. AND A MORON. I WILL TRY TO SALVAGE THIS SITUATION AS BEST I CAN. YOU CAN FEEL FREE TO POACH YOUR SMALL GAME. TRY NOT TO SCARE OFF THE BIG PREY. BIG PREY, HUH?   SO I TAKE A LEFT WHEN I REACH THE DOCKS…? THAT IS CORRECT. THANK YOU… EXCUSE ME, SER… … YES? I WAS WONDERING IF YOU COULD ASSIST ME. OKAY, PERHAPS THAT WASN'T NICE. BUT I DIDN'T TELL HIM TO TRY TO SCAM THE GENTLEMAN AT THE BAR. WELL, AS I RECALL, HOUSE QINTARA WAS RUMORED TO BE IN LEAGUE WITH THE VENATORI. AS A MEMBER OF THE MAGISTERIUM, IT WOULD PROBABLY BE MY DUTY TO LOOK INTO SUCH THINGS. MAGISTERIUM…? SO WHILE I WOULD BE HAPPY TO HELP A STRAPPING YOUNG LAD LIKE YOU ESCAPE THE CITY BEFORE ANYTHING BAD HAPPENS… … I WOULD THEN BE COMPELLED TO SEIZE ANY AND ALL ASSETS I ASSISTED IN REMOVING FROM VENTUS. ON BEHALF OF THE MAGISTERIUM. UNTIL AN INVESTIGATION RESOLVED THE ISSUE OF VENATORI INFLUENCE, OF COURSE. UM… WELL… I HAVE ALTERNATE FUNDING, SO… NOT INTERESTED? SUCH A PITY. I'D HAVE LOVED TO HELP. FOR ANDRASTE'S SAKE… RUN AWAY, YOUNG MAN. I TELL YOU TO STAY AWAY FROM THE BIG PREY. YOU IMMEDIATELY GO POACHING. AND END UP FACING DOWN A MAGISTER WHO I SIMPLY ASKED FOR DIRECTIONS. AS I SAID… A MORON. AND LIKE I SAID… WE COULD WORK TOGETHER. NO. WE ARE NOT PEERS. YOU ARE A SMALL TIME GRIFTER. I AM A PROFESSIONAL. ROUGH DATE? YOU HAVE NO IDEA. AFTER WHAT SHE DID TO ME, I DON'T THINK MY FATHER--THE MAGISTER --WILL LET ME BACK INTO OUR HOME. WHAT? WHAT DID SHE DO? HEY… WE SHOULD TALK. WHAT KIND OF LADY DESTROYS THE REPUTATION OF A MAGISTER'S SON? AND WAIT… YOUR STAFF. HOW CAN THAT EVEN CONDUCT MAGICAL ENERGIES? I SHOULD HAVE KNOWN THAT PROP-MASTER WASN'T WORTH THE COIN HE WAS PAID. I ASSURE YOU, MY STAFF IS REAL. BUT EVEN IF IT WERE FAKE… … MY MABARI IS NOT. SOMEONE'S BEEN THROUGH HERE. SEARCH FOR--URK! < NOT LONG AFTER THIS PATROL FAILS TO RETURN, THE CITY WILL KNOW WE'RE HERE. > * < THEN WE SPEED UP THE TIMETABLE. >  HOW THE FUCK…? DID I FORGET TO MENTION I TRAVEL WITH A MABARI? HER NAME IS AUTUMN. WHEN I'M IN FERELDEN, SHE'S DESCENDED FROM THE MABARI WHO FOUGHT BY THE SIDE OF THE HERO OF FERELDEN. IN THE FREE MARCHES, SHE WAS A GIFT FROM THE HAWKE FAMILY. BUT WHEREVER I GO, SHE IS QUITE HANDY AT DE-ESCALATING A BAD SITUATION. CAREFUL. SHE BITES. WHAT NOW? WE KEEP TRYING TO SCREW EACH OTHER OVER…? OR MAYBE, WE WORK TOGETHER. THIS TOWN'S GONNA FALL. MAYBE WE CAN PICK IT CLEAN, THEN WATCH EACH OTHER'S BACKS AS WE BAIL. I BELIEVE I ALREADY SAID NO. YOU KNOW WHAT YOUR PROBLEM IS? YOU THINK YOU'RE BETTER THAN ME. AND THAT IS A PROBLEM… HOW? BUT DEEP DOWN, YOU SEE IT. I'M RAW, I'M UNTRAINED. AND I STILL MATCHED YOU MOVE FOR MOVE. YOU'RE SCARED OF ME. SCARED? OF YOU? YOU'RE A CHILD. I WAS STEALING THE ARISHOK'S GENITAL PIERCINGS BEFORE YOU STOPPED WETTING YOUR NAPPIES, YOU CRETIN. WELL, IF YOU'RE SO SURE YOU'RE BETTER, YOU WANNA BET ON THAT? GO ON. WE PICK A TARGET. FIRST ONE TO CON THEM OUTOF SOMETHING-- ANYTHING-- WINS. LOSER LEAVES TOWN? DEAL. HOW ABOUT HER? THE WOMAN I SAW YOU TALKING WITH BEFORE YOU TRIED TO CON ME? NICE TRY. IT WAS JUST A QUICK TALK WITH HER-- --A QUICK FLIRT, YOU MEAN. WHAT'S THE MATTER? CAN'T SPOT THE " AMATEUR " A HEAD START? FINE. FIRST TO GET SOMETHING FROM THE GIRL OR THE BROTHER. SURE. NOW, IF YOU'LL EXCUSE ME, SHE'S HERE TO SEE ME. THE KEY HERE IS TO LET THE BOY DO MY WORK FOR ME. ALL I NEED IS THE NAMES OF THOSE TWO. OUR PARENTS HAD A LOT IN COMMON WITH YOUR FATHER. SHARED INTERESTS, IF YOU WILL. FRANCESCA, SHUSH. FLORIAN AND FRANCESCA INVIDUS? I AM MAGISTER ARAMIS, AND RIGHT NOW, YOU ARE INTERFERING IN MY INVESTIGATION. WE'RE SO SORRY… WE DIDN'T MEAN… IF YOU STAY AWAY FROM HOUSE QINTARA UNTIL THIS IS OVER, PERHAPS YOUR HOUSE CAN BE SPARED. FATHER WILL BE FURIOUS WITH YOU FOR THIS… BUT FLORIAN… I… LET ME DEAL WITH THIS MAGISTER. MY SISTER IS NAIVE. SHE TRUSTS TOO EASILY. THE VENATORI NEARLY DESTROYED TEVINTER. THE WORLD, EVEN. WE MUST FIND ALL FAMILIES WHO WERE PART OF THE GROUP --OR EVEN ASSISTED THEM. I ASSURE YOU, NEITHER FRANCESCA NOR I-- YOU KNOW HOW IT IS, ONCE A NAME IS IN A REPORT, I HAVE TO DO MY DUE DILIGENCE. CALIX…? MY BROTHER IS SPEAKING WITH THAT MAGISTER, SO WE ONLY HAVE A SHORT TIME. WE WEREN'T SURE IF YOUR FATHER IWAS WITH THE CAUSE, BUT NOW WE KNOW. I'D LIKE OUR HOUSES TO FORM AN ALLIANCE… AGAINST PERSECUTION FROM THE LUCERNI. OR ANYONE ELSE. IS THERE NOTHING I CAN DO TO MAKE THIS GO AWAY? MY SISTER AND I WOULD NOT WANT TO BLUNDER INTO ANYTHING THAT HURTS OUR FAMILY. OF COURSE. WE SHOULD TALK SOMEPLACE PRIVATE. THIS STONE CAN SERVE AS A FOCUS FOR SPECIAL MAGICKS… FRANCESCA! THANK YOU FOR THIS GIFT. I'LL SEE YOU LATER. I NEED TO WRAP THINGS UP WITH THE MAGISTER. A LOVELY GEMSTONE. USEFUL FOR MAGIC, NO? PERHAPS A DEMONSTRATION, YOUNG MASTER QINTARA? SHE IS NOT A MAGISTER! SHE'S A CON ARTIST! AND THIS YOUNG MAN IS MOST CERTAINLY NOT A QINTARA. HE IS A GRIFTER. WAIT… YOU'RE NOT…? ONE WHO DOESN'T UNDERSTAND THE RULES OF THE GAME, APPARENTLY. JULIUS! GRAB THE OTHERS! A PAIR OF CON ARTISTS HAVE JUST TRIED TO SWINDLE MY SISTER! WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU DOLTS? MAGIC KILLS MABARI SAME AS MEN. THE MABARI'S GOT THE RIGHT IDEA. NOW #HUFF#  WILL YOU JUST AGREE TO #HUFF# WORK WITH ME? OH, DO SHUT UP! GOOD GIRL! WE'LL HIDE IN THERE. AUTUMN! YOU'VE GROWN SINCE I LAST SAW YOU. MY DEAR OLIVIA… IT'S GOOD TO SEE YOU. LOOKS LIKE YOU'RE IN NEED OF SOME HELP. SO AM I. FROM BOTH OF YOU.

full_title_text: EXCUSE ME. I'M LOOKING FOR A WOMAN. HER NAME'S ELENA. WE WERE HERE AT YOUR MARKET JUST A WEEK AGO. HAVE YOU SEEN HER THIS MORNING? NO, MILORD. MANY APOLOGIES. YOU LOOKIN' FOR A TALL, ELEGANT GAL? SHORT HAIR? TRAVELS WIT' A MABARI PUPPY? YES. THAT'S HER. YOU'VE SEEN HER? ANYTHING OF VALUE MISSIN' THIS MORNIN'? YES, BUT THAT'S NOT-- YOU WON'T FIND HER. YOU'VE BEEN CONNED. AND ROBBED. HER NAME'S NOT ELENA, EITHER. IT'S…  HER NAME'S NOT ELENA, EITHER. IT'S… … OLIVIA PRYDE. FAILED ACTRESS. CONFIDENCE ARTIST. AS I AM A MAGISTER, PERHAPS IT'S BEST IF YOU LEAVE THIS MATTER TO ME, EH? BUT THESE TWO, THEY-- THEY WILL BE DEALT WITH, BUT NOT BY YOU, DEAR BOY. I SEE YOU'RE UP TO THE SAME OLD TRICKS. MY FRIEND CAN MAKE THAT PROBLEM GO AWAY. IF YOU PUT YOUR SKILLS TO USE FOR ME. MY ASSOCIATE NEEDS TO RETRIEVE SOMETHING FROM THE QINTARA ESTATE. SHE CAN BREAK INTO ANY-PLACE. SER AARON FLATTERS ME. IF SHE HAS ENOUGH INFORMATION TO WORK. THE BOY CLAIMS TO BE A QINTARA. IF HE'S WITH YOU, THEN HE CLEARLY IS A LIAR. HOWEVER, BETWEEN THE TWO OF YOU, IT SEEMS SAFE TO ASSUME YOU CAN SECURE THE FLOOR PLANS TO THE ESTATE. FOR THE SAKE OF ARGUMENT, WHAT HAPPENS IF WE DON'T HELP? MY FRIEND THE MAGISTER TURNS YOU OVER TO THOSE MEN WHO WERE CHASING YOU. THIS WILL TAKE US BACK TO THE INN. YOU TWO CAN PLAN YOUR NEXT STEPS THERE. DRINKS ON YOU? IF THAT GETS YOU TO AGREE, SURE. I'M IMPRESSED. FINDING THE BACK WAY OUT OF THE INN WHERE YOU'RE STAYING HARDLY SEEMED YOUR STYLE ALL THOSE YEARS AGO. THAT'S MY SQUIRE'S INFLUENCE. SO YOUR NAME IS OLIVIA, HUH? WE'RE NOT HERE TO CHAT, MY BOY. WE'VE BEEN GIVEN A TASK, AND THE COVER YOU'VE CHOSEN FOR YOURSELF IS OUR BEST CHANCE OF GETTING IT DONE QUICKLY. GONNA BE TOUGH TO GET INFO ON THE QINTARA ESTATE. NOBODY'S BEEN IN THERE FOR AT LEAST TEN YEARS. WHAT DO YOU KNOW OF THE PLACE? NOT MUCH. WAS DECLARED A LANDMARK A WAYS BACK. THE QINTARA FAMILY HAS BEEN IMPORTANT SINCE THE START OF THE IMPERIUM. A LANDMARK? THAT MEANS THE ESTATE'S FLOOR PLANS HAVE TO BE KEPT IN OFFICIAL CITY RECORDS… YEAH, AT THE CITY'S VAULT. THAT'D BE HARDER TO BREAK INTO THAN THE ESTATE. BREAK INTO? YES. TALK OUR WAY INTO? MUCH EASIER. AFTER ALL. YOU'RE A QINTARA. I DUNNO. I'M GOOD AT TALKING TO PEOPLE WHO DON'T HAVE ANY AUTHORITY. LIKE THAT GORGEOUS LITTLE MAGE. PEOPLE AT THE VAULT WILL SEE RIGHT THROUGH ME. OH? I THOUGHT YOU ASPIRED TO BE A PROFESSIONAL. INSTEAD, YOU'RE SATISFIED JUST BEING A COMMON GRIFTER. COMMON GRIFTER PUTS FOOD IN MY BELLY. BUT YOU COULD BE SO MUCH MORE. A JOB LIKE THIS, DESPITE THE RUSHED CIRCUMSTANCES, CAN BE THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN WHAT YOU DO… AND WHAT I DO. ALE. ALE? FOR ME? SER AARON, YOU SHOULDN'T HAVE. YOU HAVEN'T TOUCHED A DROP SINCE STARKHAVEN. WHAT'S THE STORY WITH THIS OLIVIA? VAEA… THE LIFE I'VE LED… IT'S NOT A SOLITARY ONE, TO BE SURE. I'VE MADE FRIENDS, ADVENTURED WITH OTHERS. AND NOW I HAVE YOU. A PARTNER. AND SOMEONE TO TEACH. BUT THERE'S NEVER BEEN TIME FOR ROMANCE. IN ALL MY YEARS, I'VE ONLY FALLEN IN LOVE ONCE. BUT I WAS A DRUNK. AND A FOOL. WELL, AT LEAST YOU'RE NOT A DRUNK ANY MORE. FAIR ENOUGH. ABSOLUTELY UNACCEPTABLE! FLORIAN, LEAVE IT BE. THE ORB IS GONE. THE MAGISTER WILL DEAL WITH THIS, AND IF WE GET IT BACK, WONDERFUL. IF NOT-- IF NOT, FATHER WILL BE FURIOUS. YOU SHOULD NEVER HAVE SPOKEN WITH THAT CHARLATAN. BROTHER, I AM SO SORRY. I REALLY THOUGHT WE COULD TRUST HIM. FRANCESCA, YOU ARE ONE OF THE MOST POWERFUL MAGES I KNOW. BUT YOU HAVE NEVER BEEN A STRATEGIST. THIS IS WHY FATHER AND I LEFT YOU OUT OF THE VENATORI. THAT " CALIX QINTARA " IS A HANDSOME MAN, WITH A LEAN BUILD, AND WE BOTH KNOW THAT IS YOUR WEAKNESS. HIS LOOKS HAD NOTHING TO DO WITH IT. I THOUGHT FATHER WOULD APPRECIATE A CONNECTION WITH HOUSE QINTARA. I THOUGHT YOU BOTH WOULD. I WAS WRONG TO BLAME YOU, FRANCESCA. FORGIVE ME. THE MAN WAS A PROFESSIONAL LIAR, AND ANYONE COULD HAVE BEEN FOOLED. THAT OTHER ONE HAD ME FOOLED AS WELL. THEY ARE BOTH DANGEROUS. AND EVIL. THAT IS WHY THEY CANNOT BE LEFT UNATTENDED. WHAT IF THEY FOOL MAGISTER PAVUS AS WELL? FLORIAN, DON'T-- NEVER FEAR, I'LL RETRIEVE THE FOCUSING GEM SO FATHER WILL NEVER FIND OUT. AND BOTH OF THOSE ROGUES WILL PAY. WITH THEIR LIVES. GOOD NEWS. I FOUND A DISTRACTION. IT'LL MAKE ME GOING INTO THE VAULT EASIER. THOSE TWO I SAW YOU GO UPSTAIRS WITH? STAY AWAY FROM THEM. THEY SEEM LIKE TROUBLE. MAYBE. BUT THEY'LL CREATE A DISTRACTION. ALL I HAVE TO DO IS TAKE A LEDGER FROM THE VAULTS WHILE I'M IN THERE. A DISTRACTION? DID THEY SAY WHAT KIND? THIS IS A MISTAKE. BUT… THIS IS A TOUGH JOB, AND I GOT US HELP. IT MIGHT VERY WELL BE USEFUL. BUT IT MAY ALSO GET SOMEONE KILLED. WAIT HERE. MAY I HELP YOU? NICE ACCENT. ANTIVAN, NO? SO, MY GUESS IS YOU TWO ARE CROWS. WE ARE TRADERS, IN TOWN FOR A QUICK TRANSACTION. INVOLVING A… LEDGER, WAS IT? THE YOUNG MAN SPOKE WITH YOU. IS THERE A PROBLEM WITH OUR OFFER? NO. NO PROBLEM AT ALL. BUT THIS DISTRACTION YOU CREATE? IT CAN'T BE A VIOLENT ONE. IF WE GET THE JOB DONE, AND ENABLE YOU TO DO THE SAME, WHY DO YOU CARE? BECAUSE I PREFER NOT TO KILL. I LOATHE THAT KIND OF WORK. UGLY AND PETTY. SO. IF YOU WISH US TO RETRIEVE THIS LEDGER, YOU CANNOT KILL OR HURT ANYONE TO CREATE THE DISTRACTION. WE DON'T WANT TROUBLE, ANY MORE THAN YOU DO. DEAL. WONDERFUL. SEE? I THINK WE'LL GET ALONG SMASHINGLY. THIS IS WHAT WE GET FOR WORKING WITH AMATEURS. I LIKE HER. I KNEW IT. KNEW WHAT? YOU DO HAVE MORALS. YOU HEARD THAT? THE IMPORTANT PARTS. YOU TOOK A STAND. DID WHAT WAS RIGHT. HARDLY THE ACTIONS OF A MERE LIAR. I JUST DIDN'T WANT ANYONE TO DIE. A MORAL STANCE. WHY SO CONCERNED ABOUT MY MORALITY? BRAVE SER KNIGHT… ARE YOU TRYING TO REDEEM ME? I " FACILITATE " CRIMES AGAINST WEALTHY NOBLES AND ACT AS A GO-BETWEEN FOR THE SALE OF THE " PROCEEDS. " LADY OLIVIA USUALLY PILFERS ITEMS OF VALUE FROM UNSUSPECTING NOBLES. SHE SELLS THEM TO ME. I SELL' EM ELSEWHERE, AND MY PROFITS GO TO FEED THE POOR. MY FIFTEEN COUSINS. DIRT POOR, THEY ARE. I BOUGHT THIS OFF HER. ONLY AFTER I'D PAID DID I GIVE IT A GOOD LOOK. I REALIZED THAT SHE'D STOLEN FROM SER AARON HAWTHORNE. LANDLESS KNIGHT. NO WEALTH TO SPEAK OF ONE OF US. THE TYPE OF MARK I WOULD NEVER TARGET. SO I'M GIVING THIS BACK TO YOU. SER AARON? EVERYTHING OKAY? THEY SAY YOU LEFT THE PALACE IN A HURRY? KING ALISTAIR, MY APOLOGIES. LADY ELENA LEFT, AND I WAS WORRIED. WILL THIS AFFECT YOUR TRIP TO EDGEHALL? WE CAN DELAY IT. NO, YOUR HIGHNESS. I WILL LEAVE TOMORROW. ANY TROUBLE HERE? JUST A MERCHANT, MY KING. I WILL JOIN YOU FOR LUNCH ONCE MY BUSINESS IS DONE. WHAT YOU JUST DID? ONE OF MANY REASONS I'M HAPPY TO EAT THIS LOSS, SER AARON. HOWEVER, IF YOU SEE LADY OLIVIA PRYDE AGAIN… TELL HER SHE'S DEAD TO ME. YOU WORKED WITH SLIM COULDRY FOR YEARS, DIDN'T YOU? KNEW HIS FEELINGS ON NOBILITY. YOU HAD TO KNOW HE WOULD REALIZE THE PENDANT WAS MINE. YOU HAD TO KNOW HE'D GIVE IT BACK, MAKE NO MONEY ON THE DEAL. AND THAT YOU WOULD END UP STEALING HIS MONEY, BUT NOTHING FROM ME. NOTHING PHYSICAL AT LEAST. YES. I KNEW IT. AND I WANTED YOU TO HAVE IT BACK. LET'S NOT MAKE A FUSS OVER IT, THOUGH. I KNEW IT.   I KNEW YOU WERE MORE THAN  A COMMON THIEF, ELENA.     MY NAME IS OLIVIA. AND DON'T KNOCK ME BEING A THIEF YOU TRAVEL WITH ONE NOW, DON'T YOU? BESIDES… I AM ANYTHING BUT COMMON.   STILL NOTHING? YOU AND I BOTH KNOW, THE PATROL IS NOT COMING BACK. THIS CITY IS DOOMED. WE CAN USE THAT. YOU KNOW WHAT YOU'RE TO SAY? WE'VE BEEN OVER IT TEN TIMES. TEN IS HARDLY ENOUGH FOR A JOB LIKE THIS. JUST LOOK AT THAT VAULT. WELCOME TO VAULT. HOW MAY I ASSIST YOU? I AM MAGISTER ARAMIS, AND THIS YOUNG MAN IS CALIX QINTARA. THIS MAN KNOWS WHO I AM. WE SHARED DRINKS LAST NIGHT. AND QUITE A NIGHT IT WAS, EH? THAT IT WAS, GOOD SER. GOOD, THEN YOU CAN LET HIM PASS. I HAVE REQUESTED HE ESCORT ME TO THE QINTARA HOLDINGS IN THE VAULT. OF COURSE, MAGISTER. WE'LL JUST NEED TO SEE THE KEY ISSUED TO HIS FAMILY. THE PATROL HAS NOT RETURNED. AND THE SOLDIERS HAVE ABANDONED THIS CITY. THEY SAY THE CITY IS SURROUNDED. THE QUNARI WILL STRIKE WITHIN A DAY. I SAW MINISTERS FROM THE VAULT FLEEING THIS MORNING. MY FRIEND SAID ONE OF THEM STOLE HIS COIN AND USED IT TO PAY FOR A SHIP BOUND FOR MINRATHOUS! MY BOX! I WANT TO CHECK IT NOW! I'D LIKE TO TAKE ALL MY GOODS! IF YOU'LL ALL JUST CALM DOWN. YOU'D BEST GET INSIDE, YOUNG MASTER QINTARA. MAY I HELP YOU? I AM CALIX QINTARA. I SHOWED THE GUARD MY KEY, AND THIS… CHAOS DESCENDED. HE WENT TO QUELL IT. TOOK MY KEY, TOO. OH. UH… IF YOU'LL JUST WAIT HERE… YOUNG WOMAN, I AM A MAGISTER. AND THIS YOUNG MAN NEEDS TO SHOW ME HIS FAMILY'S ARCHIVES. THAT NONSENSE OUT FRONT WILL TAKE ALL DAY TO SORT OUT. THE RUMORS ABOUT THIS CITY ARE TRUE. IT IS SURROUNDED, AND WILL FALL. LEAVING WILL BE DIFFICULT. BUT IF YOU WAIT FOR ME, I PROMISE YOU, LADY OLIVIA PRYDE. YOU WILL LEAVE THIS TOWN SAFELY. RIGHT, WELL, I GUESS WE'RE DRINKING NOW. THE WAY YOU SWOOPED IN THERE? TALKING ALL MAGISTER-EY? AMAZING. YOU DID QUITE WELL, YOURSELF. FOR A MORON, YOU MEAN. YES. FOR A MORON. SO, OLIVIA PRYDE…? THAT'S YOUR REAL NAME? YES, AND DAMN SER AARON FOR SHARING IT WITH YOU. LET ME GUESS… YOURS IS ACTUALLY… CALIX. I KNOW. SLOPPY. AND AMATEURISH. BUT I DIDN'T ADOPT THE QINTARA NAME TO SCAM PEOPLE.
